264
00:14:16,826 --> 00:14:18,863
Nu, e Cupa Feris.

265
00:14:19,590 --> 00:14:23,780
Feris va juca „Rai-Net Access
Battlers” cu toată lumea.

266
00:14:24,276 --> 00:14:25,486
Kyouma!

267
